Shoes.ShoeDescription: The Nike Dunk Low ‘Black White’ also known as 'Panda' treats the retro model to an essential two-tone color scheme that accentuates the sneaker’s clean lines, developed by designer Peter Moore
The adidas Yeezy Foam Runner ‘Onyx’ applies a sleek monochrome finish to the futuristic slip-on. Black injected EVA foam is utilized on the molded one-piece upper to maximize airflow.
The adidas Yeezy Boost 700 ‘Hi-Res Blue’ showcases eye-catching hues on the chunky lifestyle runner and the vibrant hues are offset by a contrasting black suede mudguard
The Pharrell x NMD Human Race Trail ‘Sun Glow’ release in November of 2017 and is built with lightweight Primeknit construction in teal, supported by a stabilizing lace cage in EQT Yellow.
